-NYC Climate Strike 2019-
And this is how powerful, intelligent, and brave our future is 💚

It's crazy to think about how socially, environmentally, and politically conscious these children are. Imagine being this aware at such a young age. If they can face the truth so can you. So follow in their footsteps. Following young activists like Greta Thunberg, Xiuhtexcatl Martinez, Alexandria Villasenor, Isra Hirsi and all the youth that showed up around the world today. They have something to say and we won't stop until it's heard.
